       Surefire reports for EUnit (Format used by Maven and Atlassian Bamboo
       for example to integrate test results). Based on initial code from Paul
       Guyot.

       Example: Generate XML result file in the current directory:

            eunit:test([fib, eunit_examples],
                       [{report,{eunit_surefire,[{dir,"."}]}}]).

